WHEN YOU FINALLY GET YOUR CANADIAN PR (PERMANENT RESIDENCY) AFTER YEARS OF WAITING 😭🥰🥹🥳 
.
It might not seem like a big deal to some but I literally feel like I can breathe easier now that I don’t have to constantly worry about updating permits/visas and staying on top of paperwork and not being eligible for so many opportunities. I’ve been in Canada almost 8 years and Josh has been here 6.5 years so it’s been a long (frustrating and costly too) journey to get to this point but I’m so glad it’s finally over. To all my immigrant friends, there is light at the end of the tunnel (even though it might not feel like it sometimes!). Hang in there and my DMs are always open if you’re navigating this process and wanna chat 💛 
.
